Bresnan Broadband Holdings, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 23, 2017 6:44 AM ET
Media

Company Overview of Bresnan Broadband Holdings, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
As of July 1, 2013, Bresnan Broadband Holdings, LLC was acquired by Charter Communications Operating, LLC. Bresnan Broadband Holdings, LLC, together with its subsidiaries, owns and operates cable television systems in Colorado, Wyoming, Montana, and Utah. The company’s services include video, high-speed data, voice over Internet protocol, and commercial video services, as well as data and voice services. It also provides broadband telecommunications services. As of December 31, 2012, it served approximately 370,000 total customers, 304,000 video subscribers, 292,000 high-speed data customers, and 170,000 voice customers. The company is based in Purchase, New York.


1 Manhattanville RoadPurchase, NY 10577United States



Phone: 914-641-3300

Fax: 914-641-3301








