Bresnan Broadband Holdings, LLC To Host Bondholder Conference Call






Business Wire




Feb 28, 2012 10:00 AM EST













 


























































  Bresnan Broadband Holdings, LLC will host a conference call on Friday, March 2, 2012 at 10:00 a.m. Eastern time for its bondholders to discuss the information contained in its fourth quarter and full year 2011 financial statements available on Cablevision’s investor relations website prior to the call at http://www.cablevision.com/investor/bbh.jsp .  To participate, please dial 800-895-1085 with conference ID BRESNAN approximately 10 minutes prior to the call.  Bresnan Broadband Holdings, LLC is a subsidiary of Cablevision Systems Corporation (NYSE:CVC), one of the nation’s leading media and telecommunications companies. Additional information about Cablevision Systems Corporation is available on the Web at www.cablevision.com.    



 



 










































